      "created_at": "2021-02-06T17:07:09.562Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Regarding this topic, I have a different setup and can\u2018t really use the sound alerts. I\u2018m watching netflix on Apple TV and my headphones are connected to this ATV. TrainerDay is running on the iPad. It\u2018s impossible to hear the sound of the iPad while I\u2018m watching a movie with headphones on the ATV <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"></p>\n<p>Would it be possible to make a visual signal like black/white blinking of the screen a few seconds before an interval.</p>\n<p>I know, first world problems <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/wink.png?v=9\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wink:\"> It\u2018s just an idea and maybe there are hearing-impaired cyclists that would also benefit from a visual solution.</p>",
